00:15:41.719 --> 00:15:47.640
And teaching did. So I freelanced, I taught, I taught for Posit as well. And here I am.

00:15:47.640 --> 00:15:51.400
I started attending the Hangout in 2021 when Rachel started it and I did not stop.

