but he's in the camera on crew and he was waving, so he outed himself.

00:36:28.044 --> 00:36:30.803
Brian's flattery or maybe I did say his last name.

00:36:32.044 --> 00:36:34.803
So, yes, I think that that that curiosity,

00:36:35.003 --> 00:36:38.924
willingness to check in with people, lack of ego, all of that is so important.

